    "Title": "Trigger A Trap",
    "Description": "Some asshole going by the name ~mission(TargetName) has been running a scheme where their cargo ship requests refueling services only to ambush our ships when they get there. Even loaded the damn thing up with real cargo to make sure it passes scans. We\u2019ve spread the word so nobody in Rough & Ready will fall for the trap again, but I want this skag punished. \n\nI think ~mission(TargetName|Last) knows a lot of our people on sight, so I\u2019m guessing it\u2019ll be better to pay you to take care of it. Heard that they were spotted around ~mission(Location|Address). Head there now and take care of that cargo ship and anyone protecting it once and for all. \n\n- Smokey",
